Feature	Description
✅ Bookmarklet	Paste into a browser bookmark, click on any site
🔍 JS/HTML Scan	Parses inline HTML and loaded JS files
🧪 Regex Signatures	Detects common API keys, tokens, and secrets
💾 Save to TXT	Downloads a report with all hits
🧛 Thematic	It’s creepy, kooky, and Dracula-approved

